{"tid":1851512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果眾籌畀辭職嘅醫護人員","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:40:49.000Z","uid":38885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbda5651ac730d064572b15e82278da7c832377","tid":1851512,"uid":38885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"有無人會夾錢"},{"pid":"f921edf05bc34128f825f46128e2adb472027b1c","tid":1851512,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=3ee9d038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"08cf5ae1ca6c1f7a6383e59946aa29a6613a5615","tid":1851512,"uid":81006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"等大家一齊搵到口罩先至再搞呢啲無謂嘢啦<br />\n人哋做護士大把錢啦使鬼你幫手"},{"pid":"355bb2b89eee596e49f79759a1923529b43e8130","tid":1851512,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"會夾，兩個月糧一定要比番罷工醫護，然後就係每月生活費用，至少有一年生活費支援服務。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddb0a569a29e07f6bc1664a753192cd4f262c3a","tid":1851512,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥 借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"bb9dca826fe0414dab500a5377ad7522c512bab1","tid":1851512,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7cbda5651ac730d064572b15e82278da7c832377","tid":1851512,"uid":38885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"有無人會夾錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"冇呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"f50c1ef03e52c88f3b109617f6b021d155d224fd","tid":1851512,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"勞工法例<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/text_alternative/pdf/tc/09.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftext_alternative%2Fpdf%2Ftc%2F09.pdf&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=704bc45c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/text_alternative/pdf/tc/09.pdf</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">僱員</span></strong></span>在以下情況，亦可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">即時終止僱傭合約</span></span></strong>，而<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無須預先通知</span></span></strong>或給予代通<br />\n知金：<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合理地恐懼身體會受到暴力或疾病的危害；</span></strong></span><br />\n2. 受僱主苛待；或<br />\n3. 已為僱主連續工作不少於 5 年，而經註冊醫生或註冊中醫發出指定<br />\n的證明書，證明永久不適合擔任現時的工作（請參閱第十一章）。"}]}